<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Mirror"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Porter Robinson"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Nurture"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1839137993"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1473326229"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USQE92000090"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="235518886"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="chan-air"/></metadata></head><body dur="05:03.072"><div begin="00:35.287" end="05:03.072"><p begin="00:35.287" end="00:39.582" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L0"><span begin="00:35.287" end="00:35.507">Well,</span> <span begin="00:35.507" end="00:35.962">you</span> <span begin="00:35.962" end="00:36.397">were</span> <span begin="00:36.397" end="00:36.597">the</span> <span begin="00:36.597" end="00:37.472">af</span><span begin="00:37.472" end="00:37.682">ter</span><span begin="00:37.682" end="00:39.582">math</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">的确 所有的指责和批评</span></p><p begin="00:39.582" end="00:43.072" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:39.582" end="00:39.879">Of</span> <span begin="00:39.879" end="00:40.423">e</span><span begin="00:40.423" end="00:40.908">very</span> <span begin="00:40.908" end="00:41.753">judg</span><span begin="00:41.753" end="00:43.072">ment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">都创伤在了你内心</span></p><p begin="00:43.847" end="00:47.172" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:43.847" end="00:44.107">So</span> <span begin="00:44.107" end="00:44.532">cold</span> <span begin="00:44.532" end="00:44.927">by</span> <span begin="00:44.927" end="00:45.157">the</span> <span begin="00:45.157" end="00:45.987">sweat</span> <span begin="00:45.987" end="00:47.172">that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的付出似乎毫无意义</span></p><p begin="00:48.072" end="00:49.997" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:48.072" end="00:48.362">You'll</span> <span begin="00:48.362" end="00:48.762">waste</span> <span begin="00:48.762" end="00:49.237">a</span><span begin="00:49.237" end="00:49.997">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">以至于你虚度着光阴</span></p><p begin="00:52.006" end="00:56.346" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:52.006" end="00:52.598">And</span> <span begin="00:52.598" end="00:53.190">you</span> <span begin="00:53.190" end="00:53.781">car</span><span begin="00:53.781" end="00:54.176">ry</span> <span begin="00:54.176" end="00:54.965">your</span> <span begin="00:54.965" end="00:55.162">e</span><span begin="00:55.162" end="00:55.557">ne</span><span begin="00:55.557" end="00:56.346">mies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你与敌人并肩前行</span></p><p begin="00:56.346" end="01:00.432" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:56.346" end="00:56.991">But</span> <span begin="00:56.991" end="00:58.281">they're</span> <span begin="00:58.281" end="00:58.712">so</span> <span begin="00:58.712" end="00:59.142">fa</span><span begin="00:59.142" end="00:59.572">mi</span><span begin="00:59.572" end="01:00.432">liar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但他们甚至更了解你</span></p><p begin="01:00.432" end="01:04.708" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="01:00.432" end="01:00.907">I'm</span> <span begin="01:00.907" end="01:01.857">sick</span> <span begin="01:01.857" end="01:02.332">of</span> <span begin="01:02.332" end="01:03.045">the</span> <span begin="01:03.045" end="01:03.758">com</span><span begin="01:03.758" end="01:04.233">pa</span><span begin="01:04.233" end="01:04.708">ny</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我受够了这萦绕的伴羁</span></p><p begin="01:04.708" end="01:07.301" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:04.708" end="01:05.054">So</span> <span begin="01:05.054" end="01:05.227">I</span> <span begin="01:05.227" end="01:05.918">cull</span> <span begin="01:05.918" end="01:06.437">the</span> <span begin="01:06.437" end="01:07.301">shame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为此我蒙蔽了羞耻之心</span></p><p begin="01:07.651" end="01:11.986" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:07.651" end="01:08.115">And</span> <span begin="01:08.115" end="01:08.270">I</span> <span begin="01:08.270" end="01:08.890">know</span> <span begin="01:08.890" end="01:09.664">you'll</span> <span begin="01:09.664" end="01:10.128">say</span> <span begin="01:10.128" end="01:10.593">how</span> <span begin="01:10.593" end="01:10.902">I'm</span> <span begin="01:10.902" end="01:11.057">a</span> <span begin="01:11.057" end="01:11.522">bur</span><span begin="01:11.522" end="01:11.986">den</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道你会说是我拖累了你</span></p><p begin="01:11.986" end="01:16.107" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:11.986" end="01:12.673">Yeah,</span> <span begin="01:12.673" end="01:13.016">do</span> <span begin="01:13.016" end="01:13.703">your</span> <span begin="01:13.703" end="01:14.562">worst,</span> <span begin="01:14.562" end="01:15.077">all</span> <span begin="01:15.077" end="01:15.420">at</span> <span begin="01:15.420" end="01:16.107">once</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那就将你的负面情绪一次性发泄出去</span></p><p begin="01:16.107" end="01:20.443" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:16.107" end="01:16.262">I</span> <span begin="01:16.262" end="01:16.881">know</span> <span begin="01:16.881" end="01:17.501">what</span> <span begin="01:17.501" end="01:17.965">you</span> <span begin="01:17.965" end="01:18.585">want</span> <span begin="01:18.585" end="01:19.204">from</span> <span begin="01:19.204" end="01:19.514">me,</span> <span begin="01:19.514" end="01:20.133">from</span> <span begin="01:20.133" end="01:20.443">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道你想让我做出的退让</span></p><p begin="01:20.443" end="01:24.626" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:20.443" end="01:20.582">I</span> <span begin="01:20.582" end="01:21.140">know</span> <span begin="01:21.140" end="01:21.698">what</span> <span begin="01:21.698" end="01:22.395">you're</span> <span begin="01:22.395" end="01:22.953">thin</span><span begin="01:22.953" end="01:23.511">king,</span> <span begin="01:23.511" end="01:24.068">thin</span><span begin="01:24.068" end="01:24.626">king</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我也了解你无比挣扎的内心</span></p><p begin="01:24.626" end="01:29.134" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:24.626" end="01:25.062">And</span> <span begin="01:25.062" end="01:25.499">it's</span> <span begin="01:25.499" end="01:25.935">not</span> <span begin="01:25.935" end="01:26.371">the</span> <span begin="01:26.371" end="01:27.098">voice</span> <span begin="01:27.098" end="01:27.389">of</span> <span begin="01:27.389" end="01:27.825">all</span> <span begin="01:27.825" end="01:28.261">the</span> <span begin="01:28.261" end="01:28.407">o</span><span begin="01:28.407" end="01:29.134">thers</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">尽管这并非是所有声音的意愿</span></p><p begin="01:29.134" end="01:33.225" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:29.134" end="01:29.952">You've</span> <span begin="01:29.952" end="01:30.279">on</span><span begin="01:30.279" end="01:30.607">ly</span> <span begin="01:30.607" end="01:31.261">said</span> <span begin="01:31.261" end="01:31.589">it</span> <span begin="01:31.589" end="01:31.916">to</span> <span begin="01:31.916" end="01:32.570">your</span><span begin="01:32.570" end="01:33.225">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为这只是你对自己的期许</span></p><p begin="01:33.225" end="01:37.397" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:33.225" end="01:33.374">I</span> <span begin="01:33.374" end="01:33.970">know</span> <span begin="01:33.970" end="01:34.566">what</span> <span begin="01:34.566" end="01:35.013">you</span> <span begin="01:35.013" end="01:35.609">want</span> <span begin="01:35.609" end="01:36.205">from</span> <span begin="01:36.205" end="01:36.503">me,</span> <span begin="01:36.503" end="01:37.099">from</span> <span begin="01:37.099" end="01:37.397">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我深知你盼望着我所要到达的高度</span></p><p begin="01:37.397" end="01:39.303" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:37.397" end="01:37.484">I</span> <span begin="01:37.484" end="01:37.830">know</span> <span begin="01:37.830" end="01:38.177">what</span> <span begin="01:38.177" end="01:38.610">you're</span> <span begin="01:38.610" end="01:38.956">thin</span><span begin="01:38.956" end="01:39.303">king</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:39.303" end="01:42.768"><span begin="01:39.303" end="01:39.611">(They</span> <span begin="01:39.611" end="01:39.919">come</span> <span begin="01:39.919" end="01:40.073">to</span> <span begin="01:40.073" end="01:40.381">feel</span> <span begin="01:40.381" end="01:40.689">like</span> <span begin="01:40.689" end="01:41.151">things</span> <span begin="01:41.151" end="01:41.459">we're</span> <span begin="01:41.459" end="01:41.690">say</span><span begin="01:41.690" end="01:41.921">ing</span> <span begin="01:41.921" end="01:42.075">to</span> <span begin="01:42.075" end="01:42.306">our</span><span begin="01:42.306" end="01:42.768">selves)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">慢慢的 就好像变成了自言自语</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你的所想早已暴露无遗</span></p><p begin="01:43.543" end="01:47.963" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:43.543" end="01:44.096">It's</span> <span begin="01:44.096" end="01:44.464">an</span> <span begin="01:44.464" end="01:45.201">inch</span> <span begin="01:45.201" end="01:45.937">from</span> <span begin="01:45.937" end="01:46.306">my</span> <span begin="01:46.306" end="01:47.042">ears</span> <span begin="01:47.042" end="01:47.226">a</span><span begin="01:47.226" end="01:47.963">gain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我耳边的低语再次响起</span></p><p begin="01:47.963" end="01:51.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:47.963" end="01:48.714">You</span> <span begin="01:48.714" end="01:50.217">should</span> <span begin="01:50.217" end="01:50.718">be</span> <span begin="01:50.718" end="01:51.469">sor</span><span begin="01:51.469" end="01:51.970">ry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你应该为此怀有歉意</span></p><p begin="01:51.970" end="01:54.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:51.970" end="01:52.184">A</span> <span begin="01:52.184" end="01:52.612">so</span><span begin="01:52.612" end="01:53.468">lemn</span> <span begin="01:53.468" end="01:54.110">man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个庄重的人</span></p><p begin="01:54.110" end="02:00.004" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:54.110" end="01:54.337">A</span> <span begin="01:54.337" end="01:55.017">bet</span><span begin="01:55.017" end="01:55.697">ter</span> <span begin="01:55.697" end="01:56.604">song</span> <span begin="01:56.604" end="01:57.057">to</span> <span begin="01:57.057" end="01:57.737">fix</span> <span begin="01:57.737" end="01:58.190">my</span> <span begin="01:58.190" end="01:59.097">prob</span><span begin="01:59.097" end="02:00.004">lems</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">和一首好歌 足以将一切治愈</span></p><p begin="02:00.174" end="02:04.498" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:00.174" end="02:00.534">I'm</span> <span begin="02:00.534" end="02:00.895">ti</span><span begin="02:00.895" end="02:01.435">red</span> <span begin="02:01.435" end="02:01.796">of</span> <span begin="02:01.796" end="02:02.516">your</span> <span begin="02:02.516" end="02:03.237">ques</span><span begin="02:03.237" end="02:03.777">tio</span><span begin="02:03.777" end="02:04.498">ning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我受够了你的质疑</span></p><p begin="02:04.498" end="02:08.640" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:k