04:57.427">for</span> <span begin="04:57.427" end="04:57.684">you</span> <span begin="04:57.684" end="04:57.856">to</span> <span begin="04:57.856" end="04:58.113">run</span> <span begin="04:58.113" end="04:58.541">those</span> <span begin="04:58.541" end="04:58.712">fi</span><span begin="04:58.712" end="04:58.969">nal</span> <span begin="04:58.969" end="04:59.226">few</span> <span begin="04:59.226" end="04:59.654">yards</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">传唤着你 坚持跑完这最后一段距离</span></p><p begin="04:59.654" end="05:01.724" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L58"><span begin="04:59.654" end="05:00.068">You're</span> <span begin="05:00.068" end="05:00.399">near</span><span begin="05:00.399" end="05:00.565">ly</span> <span begin="05:00.565" end="05:00.979">there,</span> <span begin="05:00.979" end="05:01.310">keep</span> <span begin="05:01.310" end="05:01.476">go</span><span begin="05:01.476" end="05:01.724">ing</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:01.724" end="05:03.072"><span begin="05:01.724" end="05:01.924">(Keep</span> <span begin="05:01.924" end="05:02.024">go</span><span begin="05:02.024" end="05:02.173">ing,</span> <span begin="05:02.173" end="05:02.373">keep</span> <span begin="05:02.373" end="05:02.473">go</span><span begin="05:02.473" end="05:02.623">ing,</span> <span begin="05:02.623" end="05:02.822">keep</span> <span begin="05:02.822" end="05:02.922">go</span><span begin="05:02.922" end="05:03.072">ing)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坚持不懈 奋力前进</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你就快到了 只需稍加努力</span></p><p begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L59"><span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">It</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">will</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">all</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">be</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">o</span><span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">kay</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">in</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">the</span> <span begin="05:03.072" end="05:03.072">end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">最终 所有的美好 都会如期而至</span></p></div></body></tt>